1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uskor kreće nova politička sezona, barem što se tiče Sabora jer političko ljeto je svakako iza nas, ali i što se tiče stranke Moskojima sva unutar strane izbore, meni se pridruži u studiju Marin Miletić. Dobro jutro i dobrodošlo.

2
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav Vama, svim gledateljicama i gledateljima i Nijan Televizija i Vaše programa ovdje.

3
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala gospodine Miletić. Dakle, više toga će se događati ovo ljeto, osim, naravno, nove saborske sezone i cijelog niza tema i ekonomskih, o tome ćemo i malo kasnije, kao i ovih što pratimo ovo ljeto, biće sigurno i nekakvih tiskovnih konferencija i inicijativa da se promijeni zakon i svašta.

4
00:00:48,000 --> 00:01:07,939
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto su najavljivali različiti politički aktiri različitih stranaka. Što se Vaše stranke tiče, sve nas zanima tko će zapravo voditi stranku i kako će ta stranka, u kojom smjeru će se razvijati i koji će biti njezin politički i u nekoj budućnosti, eventualno koalicijski potencijal da to ovako sumiram.

5
00:01:07,939 --> 00:01:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste dali jedan intervju za novi list, već se tu određene stvari najavili, pa da Vas ne pitamo ono što znamo, idemo spitat ono što možete dodatno pojasniti.

6
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Vi niste još uvijek nam jasno rekli planirate li se kandidirati ako sve vodi u tom smjeru. Mislim i Vaši nastup i Vaši vrlo konkretni odgovor.

7
00:01:29,939 --> 00:01:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nisam baš sigurno da sve vodi u tom smjeru, ali ja stvarno se trudim u svemu što radi biti jasan. Ne volim nikakva zavlaćenja, ne volim neke igre ispod stola, ne volim čak ni kad mi birače pravimo blesavima, možda svjesno ili nesvjesno, ne mislim sad s nekom lošom namjerom, nego želiš se predstaviti u nekoj slici i onda sve nekako govoriš zamagljeno, mutno.

8
00:01:55,260 --> 00:02:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne spada međutak od političare, uvijek sam bio jako jasan. Svatko od nas točno zna kad god nešto kaže, radili si s time možda neku kratkoročnu štetu, dugoročnu, ali ja sam stvarno bez patetike odavno odlučio govoriti istinu, slušati svoje srce, možda i tako bolje reći, gdje god me ono dovede.

9
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] I tako sam odlučio i kad sam se odlučio politički angažira u mostu i s jedne strane definitivno ja i dalje to tvrdim gdje god, dakle ne sad s vama, nego i na nekim kavama i razgovorima s ljudima,

10
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:42,620
[SPEAKER_01] da ja nisam upoznao bolju ekipu, dakle bolje momke u politici i djevojke naravno koji su tu sa ono predanjem, sa ogromnom energijom koji tu stvarno izideala svatko od nas koja god uzmete.

11
00:02:43,539 --> 00:02:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo ljudi kojima je politika dala, rješila sva egzistencijalna pitanja, bavili smo si tekako, svatko od nas imali i sređene poslove i neke privatne firme i sve,

12
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:57,280
[SPEAKER_01] ali smo odlučili se angažirati, zašto? Zato jer želimo mijenjati Hrvatsku.

13
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] Na koji način?

14
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,560
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je, evo, gledajte, meni je...

15
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, samo da zaključim nešto, nećete mi direktno odgovoriti na pitanje, hoćete li se kandidirati ili...

16
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:11,900
[SPEAKER_01] Meni stvarno je sada najvažnije da napravim se ono što mogu, kao član mosta, kao sabrski zastupnik,

17
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] da našim biračima, koji su, naravno, članovi, je li, stranke, probam razbit neke tabue, argumentirat ću,

18
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:31,979
[SPEAKER_01] i probam pokazati raciju, to je za mene, dakle, čisti raciju, dakle, i ja mislim da, ako nam je, nama koji tvrdimo da smo vjernici,

19
00:03:31,979 --> 00:03:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Bog dragi, nekako prvi naš obitelj, onda bi trebala biti Hrvatska, dakle, stvarno dobro Hrvatske, dakle, koje je dobro naroda,

20
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:42,939
[SPEAKER_01] ono što mi mislimo, sve politike vi grajite prema vrijednostnom sustavu.

21
00:03:42,939 --> 00:03:47,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo kad ljudi kažu, ajmo zaboraviti, na ovu vrativost, kako da zaboravimo, dakle, sve,

22
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:51,120
[SPEAKER_01] vi uzmite, evo, obiteljske politike, na čemu ih temeljite, na vrijednostnom sustavu,

23
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] migracijske politike, na vrijednostnom sustavu,

24
00:03:55,379 --> 00:03:59,979
[SPEAKER_01] sigurnostne politike, na vrijednostnom sustavu, mi desnica, desni centar, kažemo, čvrste granice,

25
00:03:59,979 --> 00:04:04,680
[SPEAKER_01] nema proba granice, nitko ne može bez dokumenta nos proviriti kroz naše granice,

26
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ljevica to gleda drugačije, dakle, obitelj, život, što je uopće život, od kada ga treba štititi,

27
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:14,740
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način, ulazi li mi tu u vašu slobodu ili ne, što trebamo napraviti,

28
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako se zibilirati javnost za kulturu života, dakle, od začeća do naravne smrti,

29
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:25,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ljevica kaže, eutanazija, dakle, koju god, to se htio reći, dakle, koju god uzmete stavu,

30
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:31,759
[SPEAKER_00] vrijednostni sustav se inkorporira u politike, i sad završću samo ovo misao,

31
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:34,439
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ja stvarno mislim da svatko od nas ko se baje politikom,

32
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] ako mu je dobro države prvo naroda, je li kao takvoga,

33
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:42,620
[SPEAKER_01] onda uvijek treba nekako te stranačke interese, koliko god je to teško.

34
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:44,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ali možda nemaju svi istu viziju što je dobro.

35
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:46,759
[SPEAKER_01] Slažem se iz time, da.

36
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:49,100
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je vama dobro nešto što nekome...

37
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:51,839
[SPEAKER_01] Slažem se, postoje neke, postoje ne, slažem se iz time.

38
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:57,720
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, na razini teorije netko može reći, ja mislim da je najbolje da idem sam kao Don Quixote

39
00:04:57,720 --> 00:05:03,160
[SPEAKER_01] i da idućih 20 godina jurišam na vjetrenjače, da budem oporba uvijek,

40
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:06,519
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, da me moji birači, paziteš, pa što fali nama koji smo u oporbi,

41
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:07,740
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo razgoliti do kraja.

42
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] Absolutno ništa.

43
00:05:08,819 --> 00:05:09,600
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, što, ajmo do kraja razgoliti.

44
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,600
[SPEAKER_01] To je najbolji, najkomodniji posao trenutajstvo u Hrvatski.

45
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:15,540
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, pazite, svaki dan, dakle, mislim da ovo peta godina,

46
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:23,139
[SPEAKER_01] po radu u Saboru. Dakle, madmani, okrugli stolovi, predlazi zakona.

47
00:05:23,139 --> 00:05:24,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne morate biti.

48
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje.

49
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:27,319
[SPEAKER_01] A ne moraš ni dolaziti u Sabor.

50
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:30,439
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ako imaš partiju koja malo snažnije stoji iza tebe,

51
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek ćeš biti prvi ili drugi, ući u Hrvatski Sabor,

52
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:37,279
[SPEAKER_01] plaćica jako, jako dobra, za naše uvijete, dakle, izrazito dobra.

53
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš si obnoviti kuću, kupiti novu kuću,

54
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,939
[SPEAKER_01] udignuti kredit, stan, kupiti neki bijesni auto,

55
00:05:42,939 --> 00:05:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] snimat videa, ne znam, sprdati ljude,

56
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,540
[SPEAKER_01] kupiti ta šest, ta osam,

57
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:51,459
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ja se nisam zato angažirao u politici

58
00:05:51,459 --> 00:05:53,839
[SPEAKER_01] i to ne znači da će se baciti na glavu.

59
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:55,740
[SPEAKER_01] To ne znači da prodajem, pa imam čast.

60
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:59,240
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nisam, ja sam s ulice došao i među učitelje,

61
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,740
[SPEAKER_01] vjeručitelje i u Hrvatski Sabor.

62
00:06:01,740 --> 00:06:04,220
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mi dobro znamo na ulici što znači čast

63
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:06,160
[SPEAKER_01] i nema izdaje.

64
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,259
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nismo drukeri.

65
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, s ove druge strane, dakle, stvarno se nisam angažirao

66
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:12,899
[SPEAKER_01] da budem 20 godina u oporbi, umro bi.

67
00:06:12,899 --> 00:06:14,319
[SPEAKER_01] Umro bi u Saboru, u oporbi.

68
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:17,379
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, a ajmo sad ovo konkretizirati kroz politike.

69
00:06:17,379 --> 00:06:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] Predstavite mi onda vašu viziju Hrvatske

70
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] i vašu viziju onoga politika

71
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] koje bi moz, kakav bi vi htjeli, trebao zagovrati.

72
00:06:28,699 --> 00:06:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo matematički sve razgovoriti.

73
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:31,740
[SPEAKER_01] Mijenjali bi, vidim da bi mijenjali.

74
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovako, pogledajte.

75
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] Samo mi odgovorite na pitanje.

76
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:34,660
[SPEAKER_01] Mijenjali bi.

77
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, imamo SDP.

78
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sinišu Hajdaša Dončića, potpuno pogubjenog lika.

79
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:40,420
[SPEAKER_01] Vono bi premijera.

80
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam, znači, ja stvarno nikog ne želim uvrijediti.

81
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:46,740
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, znate ono, kad vidite, neke ljude točno znate

82
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:48,100
[SPEAKER_01] imaju li taj gard ili nemaju.

83
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:50,959
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vi njeja kad vidite, znate da on je taj.

84
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:51,540
[SPEAKER_01] To podbrojan.

85
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo dođe i kaže da žali što se ikad maknulo ime Josipa Broza Tita po zagrebačkim trgovima.

86
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] To on rekao u intervju u Večernjaku.

87
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:07,759
[SPEAKER_01] I da će vratit nazivlje po drugu Titu, koji je za nas diktator, predstavnik jednog režima u Jugoslaviji, komunizma,

88
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:16,339
[SPEAKER_01] koji je Hrvate bacao po jamama, progonio po golim otoku i ubio više od šesto katoličkih svećenika i časnih sestara.

89
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:23,160
[SPEAKER_01] Šesto. Dakle, strašno. I sad lik dođe i kaže vratit ćemo nazivlje po drugu Titu i vjeronavk treba maknuti škola.

90
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:28,240
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sve ono protiv čega se borim Tito ili ono što je meni svetinja.

91
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, njega brišemo. S SDP-om ništa.

92
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imate možemo koji je gori od njega.

93
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, argumentirat ću iz moje perspektive, naravno.

94
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ljudi ne dođu u Knin ni jedne godine.

95
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,759
[SPEAKER_01] Dan pobjede, to je tvoja država.

96
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:46,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ti proslavljaš pobjedničku akciju koja je vratila okupirani teritorij.

97
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:53,319
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo su bili Četnici sa okrajina i sad ti slaviš dan u kojem su hrvatski branitelji ginuli.

98
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:55,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dali svoj život za našu slobodu.

99
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo se nalazi cijeli državni vrh i oporba i možemo nikada ne doći.

100
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to pod broj dva.

101
00:08:01,699 --> 00:08:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ide rasprava u Hrvatskom saboru o jeziku, hrvatskom jeziku.

102
00:08:05,139 --> 00:08:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] Sjedio sam tamo i to sam vidio svojim očima.

103
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,399
[SPEAKER_01] Slušao, nisam mogu vjerovat.

104
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, i kreće rasprava, dižu se zastupnici.

105
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo i kolegica, da ne utopim sada do kraja, dođe i kaže

106
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:20,120
[SPEAKER_01] kaj ćemo mi raspravljati ovim glupostima?

107
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo u klub.

108
00:08:21,019 --> 00:08:22,300
[SPEAKER_01] I oni se dignu i oduća.

109
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,899
[SPEAKER_01] Isto legitimno.

110
00:08:23,899 --> 00:08:28,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ali onda njihova Sandra Benčić potpiše deklaraciju jugoslavenskoj kulturi.

111
00:08:28,579 --> 00:08:29,939
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Sarajevska deklaracija.

112
00:08:29,939 --> 00:08:31,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je to online, ali ona je to potpisala.

113
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:34,200
[SPEAKER_01] Večernjak je to objavio na tom je potpisu.

114
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:37,580
[SPEAKER_01] O zajedničkom jeziku i kulturi Jugoslavije.

115
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dobro, dakle, ko je tu ludu?

116
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,340
[SPEAKER_01] A onda vokerske agende, rodna ideologija.

117
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:45,200
[SPEAKER_01] SDP ništa, možemo ništa.

118
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,620
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo, tko je vaš potencijal?

119
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] A pazite, mi smo stranka desnog centra.

120
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] Most je donio deklaraciju svoju, političku.

121
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] To je magna karta svake stranke.

122
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:56,080
[SPEAKER_01] I jasno smo rekli.

123
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:59,600
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kompletno, kršćanski svjetonazor nam je temelj.

124
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,080
[SPEAKER_01] Domovinski rat je svetinja.

125
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,139
[SPEAKER_01] Porezni sustavi, politike.

126
00:09:03,139 --> 00:09:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] To je naš trosko tu puno se angažirao oko toga.

127
00:09:05,179 --> 00:09:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sve smo definirali.

128
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo stranka desnog centra.

129
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] I glavni odbor stranke je prije...

130
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:13,200
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ne znam da li smo ovo ikad rekli u medijima.

131
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] Prije nekoliko mjeseci jasno i nedvosmisleno rekao

132
00:09:17,539 --> 00:09:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] da je moja stranka desnog centra

133
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:23,220
[SPEAKER_01] i da će se ići u razgovore, u suradnju

134
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] ili sa svim opcijama od centra na desnu.

135
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] I ovo što me pokušavaju neki, znate, pa onda ono...

136
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,860
[SPEAKER_01] Jer hrvati to vole.

137
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] Stavite u tabor, odmah te zalijepe negdje etiketu i to.

138
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,600
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mene umče ne zanima nikom...

139
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sima nam je to poznat.

140
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ni HDZ.

141
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,919
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mene zanima most.

142
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:40,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja ću odgovoriti na svako vaše pitanje, vrlo jasno.

143
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mene zanima moja stranka.

144
00:09:42,019 --> 00:09:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ja želim moju stranku jako.

145
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ne želim moju stranku na 6-7%.

146
00:09:45,259 --> 00:09:47,879
[SPEAKER_01] I držim da kad bi naši birači znali

147
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:50,100
[SPEAKER_01] most nikada neće slijevicu.

148
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:51,379
[SPEAKER_01] Nikada, makar nestali.

149
00:09:51,379 --> 00:09:54,759
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ako je naš politički put bio taj

150
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] pod Božom Petrovom

151
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,080
[SPEAKER_01] da doprinesemo demokraciji

152
00:09:58,080 --> 00:10:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno vjerujem da smo dijelom to učinili.

153
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:02,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ne treba si možda tepat previše,

154
00:10:02,259 --> 00:10:03,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali mislim da imamo određene zasluge.

155
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:05,240
[SPEAKER_01] I u borbi proti korupcije.

156
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,639
[SPEAKER_01] I naš Nikola Grmoja i Troskot.

157
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:09,279
[SPEAKER_01] I stvarno ekipa dobro, dobro radi.

158
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] I bulj.

159
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:12,039
[SPEAKER_01] I tijekom pandemije mi smo tu imali

160
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:14,299
[SPEAKER_01] jako čvrste stave za koje smo misli da branimo.

161
00:10:14,299 --> 00:10:15,940
[SPEAKER_01] Slobode pojedinaca sad se pokazali

162
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] da smo u pravu jeli nakon toliko vremena.

163
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi smo stranka desnog centra.

164
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:23,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ja držim da most treba biti lokomotiva.

165
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:25,899
[SPEAKER_01] Okupiti sve male stranke oko sebe.

166
00:10:25,899 --> 00:10:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, suvereniste, domino, HSP,

167
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:32,600
[SPEAKER_01] razgovarati sa Karolinom našom

168
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,399
[SPEAKER_01] Vidović-Krištoskom.

169
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:34,299
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo kontakte.

170
00:10:34,299 --> 00:10:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kompletno sve pozvati na jedan hup.

171
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,139
[SPEAKER_01] Napraviti nacionalnu platformu.

172
00:10:39,139 --> 00:10:40,379
[SPEAKER_01] I točno se zna.

173
00:10:40,379 --> 00:10:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] Most u Zagrebu.

174
00:10:41,539 --> 00:10:44,320
[SPEAKER_01] Mislimo ćemo, kako bi rekao,

175
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] nema nas, je li tako?

176
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, most u Slavoni nešto nas ima.

177
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tu je puno jači, ne znam.

178
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,220
[SPEAKER_01] Domino neka druga ekipa.

179
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:52,419
[SPEAKER_01] U Vukovaru je Pavliček.

180
00:10:52,419 --> 00:10:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo u Rijeci.

181
00:10:53,539 --> 00:10:55,059
[SPEAKER_01] Druge desnice nema, razumijete.

182
00:10:55,059 --> 00:10:57,179
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, drugi, kad smo mi sami išli

183
00:10:57,179 --> 00:10:59,200
[SPEAKER_01] do Mojski pokret, kad je bio na Vrhuncu,

184
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,559
[SPEAKER_01] na Vrhuncu, dobili su 3-4%,

185
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] nisu me mogli preći.

186
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, i vi tako se podijelite.

187
00:11:04,539 --> 00:11:06,240
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo, dakle, izaći pred narod.

188
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] Narod onda odluče.

189
00:11:07,779 --> 00:11:08,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo su floskule.

190
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,080
[SPEAKER_01] Miletić gura tamo, mi.

191
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

192
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,759
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, ljudi biraju.

193
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,879
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, pa, jel tako?

194
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:13,620
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, moj tata, mama...

195
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:15,919
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što je, samo da vam kažem,

196
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:17,879
[SPEAKER_00] što je ovdje i novinarski,

197
00:11:17,879 --> 00:11:19,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali i politički zanimljivo.

198
00:11:19,139 --> 00:11:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] I sad mi molim vas odgovorite na to pitanje.

199
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:26,700
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nakon, molim, tajnicu da razriješi i potpiše,

200
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] mi imamo jedan moz koji se gradi dugo vremena na tome nikad s HDZ-om,

201
00:11:33,539 --> 00:11:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] svjesni ste toga,

202
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] i korupcijskoj platformi.

203
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:40,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam to tako reći,

204
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,779
[SPEAKER_00] doista puno, puno je bilo tu

205
00:11:41,779 --> 00:11:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] i otkrivanje ili pokušaja,

206
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:46,080
[SPEAKER_00] otkrivanje ili adresiranja korupcijskih afera.

207
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, samo sam ja razgovarala sa šim kolegama.

208
00:11:47,259 --> 00:11:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] To će se nastaviti dalje.

209
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovaj dio, ne možete sad reći da ste prespavali dio

210
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:53,899
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem nikad s HDZ-om.

211
00:11:53,899 --> 00:11:55,799
[SPEAKER_00] U jednom trenutku dolazite vi,

212
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,120
[SPEAKER_00] ne znamo za glavnije odbore,

213
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] evo to smo sad isto saznali,

214
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] važna informacija,

215
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:01,379
[SPEAKER_00] dolazite vi i kažete, ali čekajte.

216
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi idemo, s obzirom za sljevicom, ne idemo,

217
00:12:04,139 --> 00:12:06,580
[SPEAKER_00] idemo sa svima od centra na desno,

218
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:08,639
[SPEAKER_00] što uključuju i HDZ.

219
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:11,299
[SPEAKER_00] To je bitna informacija,

220
00:12:11,299 --> 00:12:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] suprotna od onoga što je bio naravnije.

221
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je nezahvalno.

222
00:12:15,019 --> 00:12:15,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde probajte mi sad to malo parazno.

223
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:17,139
[SPEAKER_01] Hoću biti joj jasan skroz.

224
00:12:17,139 --> 00:12:19,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jako je nezahvalno pričati u drugim strankama.

225
00:12:19,019 --> 00:12:20,580
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno je jako nezahvalno.

226
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] I to znate i sami kao novinarka.

227
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:24,600
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ja iz pozicije Mosta pričam o HDZ-u,

228
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] to je čak malo glupavo.

229
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja mogu reći,

230
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] nama je, meni osobno je tu velik problem obuljen,

231
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] dakle koja je potpuno ljeva.

232
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:33,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je ljevičarka.

233
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:34,919
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, vi ne isključujete farize.

234
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, dakle, obuljen.

235
00:12:36,299 --> 00:12:38,940
[SPEAKER_01] Evo mogu samo reći ukratko za ministricu kulture,

236
00:12:38,940 --> 00:12:40,740
[SPEAKER_01] jedna od najgorih ministrica kulture,

237
00:12:40,740 --> 00:12:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] zato jer izrazito pomaže,

238
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,639
[SPEAKER_01] propagira ljevičarsku agendu.

239
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:49,139
[SPEAKER_01] Političke članove možemo,

240
00:12:49,139 --> 00:12:51,580
[SPEAKER_01] koji govore na festivalu Šibeniku na fališ.

241
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:52,399
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ljudi,

242
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:53,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je klasična agenda,

243
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:55,320
[SPEAKER_01] politički projekt ljevice

244
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,240
[SPEAKER_01] i ona to obilno financira

245
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,840
[SPEAKER_01] i mi se grozimo, dakle,

246
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] ministrice obuljen,

247
00:12:59,659 --> 00:13:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja osobno, dakle,

248
00:13:00,539 --> 00:13:02,580
[SPEAKER_01] i mnogi razmišljamo tu sličnu.

249
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:04,620
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vi mene kao mostovca,

250
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] ili, pa ajmo još,

251
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,299
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

252
00:13:06,299 --> 00:13:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] ako vi mene tjerate,

253
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,860
[SPEAKER_01] da ja biram

254
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:10,399
[SPEAKER_01] između ljevice i HDZ-a,

255
00:13:10,399 --> 00:13:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću uvijek izabra HDZ.

256
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,600
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja sam kršćanin u politici

257
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,700
[SPEAKER_01] demokršćanskog svjetorazora.

258
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:18,259
[SPEAKER_01] A što ako izaberete ništa?

259
00:13:18,259 --> 00:13:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, dobro.

260
00:13:18,820 --> 00:13:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je li moguće imati političku poziciju

261
00:13:20,899 --> 00:13:21,860
[SPEAKER_00] koju ne izaberete ništa?

262
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:22,200
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

263
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] gledajte,

264
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] i to je legitimno.

265
00:13:23,539 --> 00:13:24,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vas samo pitan,

266
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim ovako,

267
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:26,620
[SPEAKER_01] da naši birači

268
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] nas neće honorirat

269
00:13:29,019 --> 00:13:30,940
[SPEAKER_01] da budemo 30 godina oporba.

270
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:32,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ove fore,

271
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,740
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo sada 500 tisuća ljudi

272
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,240
[SPEAKER_01] s Tomsona glasaće za most,

273
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,779
[SPEAKER_01] imat ćemo 60 mandata.

274
00:13:37,779 --> 00:13:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

275
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,080
[SPEAKER_01] meni je to tako neozbiljno

276
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:44,299
[SPEAKER_01] da bolje ovdje da stanem.

277
00:13:44,299 --> 00:13:44,779
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

278
00:13:44,779 --> 00:13:46,620
[SPEAKER_01] treba biti razborit uvijek u politici.

279
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] To ne znači da mi sebe dajemo,

280
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:51,879
[SPEAKER_01] da ne upotrebim neku prljavu riječ prodajemo.

281
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:53,700
[SPEAKER_01] Pa rađe bi nestali,

282
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:55,379
[SPEAKER_01] neko izdali neke naše ideale,

283
00:13:55,379 --> 00:13:56,259
[SPEAKER_01] svjetonazore,

284
00:13:56,259 --> 00:13:58,080
[SPEAKER_01] poglede na svijet i ostalo.

285
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ali,

286
00:13:58,519 --> 00:13:59,299
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

287
00:13:59,299 --> 00:14:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] izađeš na izbore sa 5-6 stranaka desnice.

288
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:05,799
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo ti onda koji se namećemo narodu,

289
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] narod zna da ne držimo figu džepu.

290
00:14:07,779 --> 00:14:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] I ljudi koji izlaze na izbore,

291
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] a našeg su svjetonazora,

292
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] ne pričam ja uopće sad o Ljevice i o drugim ljudima.

293
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,159
[SPEAKER_01] Oni nisu moj problem, jeli?

294
00:14:14,159 --> 00:14:15,559
[SPEAKER_01] I ljudi znaju

295
00:14:15,559 --> 00:14:17,899
[SPEAKER_01] most je lokomotiva,

296
00:14:17,899 --> 00:14:20,080
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, cijele ove nacionalne priče

297
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,379
[SPEAKER_01] neće izdat,

298
00:14:21,379 --> 00:14:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] neće ići s Ljevicom

299
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:24,879
[SPEAKER_01] i bit će jasni u pogledu traženja

300
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:27,279
[SPEAKER_01] mi bi točno po moje nekoj vizi izašli s točka.

301
00:14:27,279 --> 00:14:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, što mi želimo?

302
00:14:28,139 --> 00:14:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] U obrazovnom sustavu,

303
00:14:29,679 --> 00:14:30,860
[SPEAKER_01] u granicama,

304
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] u sigurnosnom sustavu,

305
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,820
[SPEAKER_01] u poreznom sustavu

306
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:36,259
[SPEAKER_01] i u, ne znam,

307
00:14:36,259 --> 00:14:37,759
[SPEAKER_01] na primjer, u glasovanju,

308
00:14:37,759 --> 00:14:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] elektronskom glasovanju,

309
00:14:40,759 --> 00:14:42,759
[SPEAKER_01] možda godina za glasače

310
00:14:42,759 --> 00:14:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] i to, i mi ispod toga ne idemo.

311
00:14:44,340 --> 00:14:45,379
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ako netko neće,

312
00:14:45,379 --> 00:14:46,320
[SPEAKER_01] aj, daj ponovo izbore,

313
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,700
[SPEAKER_01] pa to onda neće biti.

314
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:48,340
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, daj ponovo,

315
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] ako vi,

316
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:51,720
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi, žele jasnoću.

317
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ljudi,

318
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:53,820
[SPEAKER_01] koliko god mi sebe

319
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] s PR,

320
00:14:54,980 --> 00:14:56,820
[SPEAKER_01] opinion makerima,

321
00:14:56,820 --> 00:14:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] možda negdje smo nekom simpatičniji,

322
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] pa nas malo više nagradi,

323
00:15:00,820 --> 00:15:02,779
[SPEAKER_01] pa nas malo nama ljepše piše,

324
00:15:02,779 --> 00:15:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] nekom dižemo živce,

325
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:05,759
[SPEAKER_01] pa ono po nama skače po glavi,

326
00:15:06,179 --> 00:15:06,639
[SPEAKER_01] ali, ok,

327
00:15:06,639 --> 00:15:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] političari smo javne,

328
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:08,580
[SPEAKER_01] smo osobe,

329
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] i moramo i na to biti sve.

330
00:15:09,539 --> 00:15:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, razumijem,

331
00:15:10,059 --> 00:15:12,759
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, cilj je okupiti zapravo desnicu,

332
00:15:12,759 --> 00:15:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] nametnuti se,

333
00:15:13,659 --> 00:15:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] vaša vizija,

334
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

335
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:18,080
[SPEAKER_00] nametnuti se kao moćan,

336
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] koalicijski partner,

337
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] i jedini ko da vidi,

338
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] i onda u biti,

339
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,700
[SPEAKER_00] imati te neke uvjete,

340
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:27,179
[SPEAKER_00] bez kojih ne biste koalirali

341
00:15:27,179 --> 00:15:28,100
[SPEAKER_00] i s HDZ-om,

342
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] naravno, ako treba.

343
00:15:29,139 --> 00:15:30,419
[SPEAKER_00] Što se tiče samo HDZ-a,

344
00:15:30,419 --> 00:15:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] samo da mi tu misl malo rastumačite,

345
00:15:33,519 --> 00:15:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] rekli ste da bi puno više voljeli

346
00:15:35,659 --> 00:15:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] surađivati s gospodinom Manušićem

347
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] nego sadašnjim predsjednikom HDZ-a,

348
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je to tako?

349
00:15:41,059 --> 00:15:43,740
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, volim ljude koji su autentični,

350
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] ovo mi je malo presvješto,

351
00:15:45,940 --> 00:15:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] i kad gledate,

352
00:15:46,559 --> 00:15:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam pet godina zastupnik,

353
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:50,159
[SPEAKER_01] sjećam se kad su mi mira bulja izbacivali,

354
00:15:50,159 --> 00:15:52,620
[SPEAKER_01] iz sabora radi pozdrava za dom spremni,

355
00:15:52,620 --> 00:15:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] izbacivali,

356
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,620
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, baš izbacivali,

357
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] govorili jako ružno o čovjeku

358
00:15:56,559 --> 00:15:57,820
[SPEAKER_01] koji je kao golo Bradimladić

359
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:58,899
[SPEAKER_01] stao na branih domovine

360
00:15:58,899 --> 00:15:59,919
[SPEAKER_01] i branio svoju zemlju,

361
00:15:59,919 --> 00:16:01,240
[SPEAKER_01] i odjednom,

362
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:04,379
[SPEAKER_01] samo transformacija u saboru,

363
00:16:04,379 --> 00:16:05,080
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bio tad,

364
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,080
[SPEAKER_01] baš u toj raspravi,

365
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] kad je krenulo branjenje,

366
00:16:07,799 --> 00:16:09,139
[SPEAKER_01] jako, dakle, pozdrava,

367
00:16:09,139 --> 00:16:10,179
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, vjerujte mi,

368
00:16:10,179 --> 00:16:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] da jednom trisetak sekundi

369
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,220
[SPEAKER_01] sam se ovako okretao,

370
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:13,559
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nije mi bilo uči pilastri,

371
00:16:13,559 --> 00:16:14,360
[SPEAKER_01] što se događa,

372
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] a onda sam shvatio mašinerija,

373
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:17,919
[SPEAKER_01] HDZ je naravno mijenjaju

374
00:16:17,919 --> 00:16:18,559
[SPEAKER_01] svoj narativ,

375
00:16:18,559 --> 00:16:20,399
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ide se skroz nekim drugim putem.

376
00:16:20,399 --> 00:16:21,919
[SPEAKER_01] Ali čini se da ga opet mijenjaju?

377
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] Što očekujete sada?

378
00:16:23,779 --> 00:16:24,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pa misli,

379
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] to stvarno nije moja briga,

380
00:16:26,019 --> 00:16:27,799
[SPEAKER_01] mi nećemo uzmaknuti niti centimetra,

381
00:16:27,799 --> 00:16:30,120
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ja neću uzmaknuti niti centimetra,

382
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] to ne znači da će se ponašat kuklao,

383
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,840
[SPEAKER_01] neki uzvikivat, vrištat,

384
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam šta,

385
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] na koncu nikad nisam mojih pet godina

386
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] koliko sam zastupnik,

387
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:40,620
[SPEAKER_01] ali niti milimetra nećemo odstupiti

388
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:43,580
[SPEAKER_01] od svjedočena ljubavi prema Bogu,

389
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:45,360
[SPEAKER_01] domovini, hrvatskim braniteljima

390
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,379
[SPEAKER_01] i ono što, ne znam,

391
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:47,779
[SPEAKER_01] znali uopće to naša javnost,

392
00:16:47,779 --> 00:16:49,820
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, za dom spremni,

393
00:16:49,820 --> 00:16:51,320
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi smo jasno osudili,

394
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, i ustaški režim,

395
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,480
[SPEAKER_01] i fašizam, i nacizam,

396
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] koliko puta,

397
00:16:54,059 --> 00:16:55,740
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam šest godina vodio svoje klinice,

398
00:16:55,740 --> 00:16:57,740
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, klince studente u Auschwitz,

399
00:16:57,740 --> 00:16:59,620
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nama je tu sve jasno,

400
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:01,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali ima ogroman ali kao kuć.

401
00:17:01,059 --> 00:17:03,240
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatska se 1991. branila,

402
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi momci iz moje ulice,

403
00:17:05,019 --> 00:17:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] iz armade su bili hosovci,

404
00:17:06,759 --> 00:17:07,700
[SPEAKER_01] Čoro i ekipa,

405
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:08,460
[SPEAKER_01] otišli su hos,

406
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, kao mulci od 18-19 godina,

407
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,200
[SPEAKER_01] neki mlađi još.

408
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:16,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ivica Jurčan je ostao bez nogu ispod koljena,

409
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] 12 dana je bio u Minskom polju,

410
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,799
[SPEAKER_01] i ona ga zarobila,

411
00:17:19,799 --> 00:17:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] završi u logoru,

412
00:17:20,579 --> 00:17:21,240
[SPEAKER_01] iz Kostrene,

413
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,279
[SPEAKER_01] Lujo Soldić, naš,

414
00:17:22,279 --> 00:17:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] joj te ljude poznajem,

415
00:17:23,559 --> 00:17:25,299
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, on vam je hosovac,

416
00:17:25,299 --> 00:17:27,319
[SPEAKER_01] koji je završio 9 mjeseci u logoru,

417
00:17:27,319 --> 00:17:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] kad je vukovar pao,

418
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, čovjeka zarobili,

419
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] i sad,

420
00:17:30,599 --> 00:17:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] Viktor Injurić Paša,

421
00:17:32,279 --> 00:17:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] pokojna Violeta Antolić,

422
00:17:33,559 --> 00:17:35,240
[SPEAKER_01] koja je nažalost poginula u prometnoj neseci,

423
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,740
[SPEAKER_01] bila je kod mene u gimnaziji u Rijeci,

424
00:17:37,059 --> 00:17:39,180
[SPEAKER_01] kao hosovka žena koja je branila vukovar,

425
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] i sada njih zaniječe,

426
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] ma nikada,

427
00:17:41,619 --> 00:17:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

428
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:43,180
[SPEAKER_01] ni pozdrav za dom spremni,

429
00:17:43,180 --> 00:17:43,660
[SPEAKER_01] ni njih,

430
00:17:43,660 --> 00:17:44,200
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

431
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] nikada,

432
00:17:44,619 --> 00:17:45,980
[SPEAKER_01] a ovo što je kipa nam,

433
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:47,779
[SPEAKER_01] što nam djeti je etikete,

434
00:17:47,779 --> 00:17:48,279
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

435
00:17:48,279 --> 00:17:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali šta,

436
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] u drugom kontekstu,

437
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] vi si zapravo druga konotacija.

438
00:17:51,460 --> 00:17:51,660
[SPEAKER_01] Pa,

439
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:53,259
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo djeca domojskog rata,

440
00:17:53,259 --> 00:17:53,779
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

441
00:17:53,779 --> 00:17:55,059
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam 94.

442
00:17:55,059 --> 00:17:57,440
[SPEAKER_01] upisao gimnaziju,

443
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:57,799
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

444
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:58,859
[SPEAKER_01] 95.

445
00:17:58,859 --> 00:18:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] je tek bila Lujada,

446
00:18:00,019 --> 00:18:01,700
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam djete domojskog rata,

447
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:02,940
[SPEAKER_01] i gledao sam iz ulice,

448
00:18:03,039 --> 00:18:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] moji prijatelji koji su išli braniti to u zemlju,

449
00:18:05,019 --> 00:18:07,279
[SPEAKER_01] neki od njih su bili pripadnici hosa.

450
00:18:07,279 --> 00:18:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znači da su drugi branitelji manje vrijedni,

451
00:18:10,119 --> 00:18:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] manje hrabri,

452
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] ma kakvi,

453
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:12,140
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

454
00:18:12,140 --> 00:18:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] od naših hajkula,

455
00:18:12,859 --> 00:18:13,859
[SPEAKER_01] specijalne policije,

456
00:18:13,859 --> 00:18:14,759
[SPEAKER_01] puma,

457
00:18:14,759 --> 00:18:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] tigrova,

458
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,319
[SPEAKER_01] vukova,

459
00:18:16,319 --> 00:18:17,799
[SPEAKER_01] da ne zaboravim sad nekoga svih,

460
00:18:17,799 --> 00:18:19,259
[SPEAKER_01] naša četvrte gardijske svih,

461
00:18:19,259 --> 00:18:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] ma ne,

462
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:20,359
[SPEAKER_01] nego,

463
00:18:20,359 --> 00:18:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] pogledajte šta se događa,

464
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja vam opet kažem iz moje perspektive,

465
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:25,759
[SPEAKER_01] mi sad gledamo takav medijski atak,

466
00:18:25,759 --> 00:18:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] na nešto što je nama,

467
00:18:28,039 --> 00:18:28,759
[SPEAKER_01] ne normalno,

468
00:18:28,759 --> 00:18:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] nego svetinja,

469
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] to su naši temelji

470
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:31,920
[SPEAKER_01] i nećemo im dopustiti da ih se dira.

471
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno,

472
00:18:32,539 --> 00:18:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] evo, dakle,

473
00:18:33,059 --> 00:18:35,299
[SPEAKER_01] napravit ćemo sve što je legitimno.

474
00:18:35,299 --> 00:18:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tko ih dira?

475
00:18:35,779 --> 00:18:37,339
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne prestaju iz dana u dan,

476
00:18:37,339 --> 00:18:37,759
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

477
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] kolumnisti,

478
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] mediji,

479
00:18:39,460 --> 00:18:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

480
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:40,700
[SPEAKER_01] ne svi naravno,

481
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:41,900
[SPEAKER_01] ne smijemo generalizirati.

482
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:42,440
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

483
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] pučka pravobraviteljica dođe i kaže,

484
00:18:44,539 --> 00:18:45,799
[SPEAKER_01] intervju u novom listu,

485
00:18:45,799 --> 00:18:46,220
[SPEAKER_01] jučer,

486
00:18:46,220 --> 00:18:47,759
[SPEAKER_01] danas sam o njoj govorio o svojim videima,

487
00:18:47,759 --> 00:18:48,660
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

488
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] pozdrav za dom spremni,

489
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:53,460
[SPEAKER_01] treba maknuti iz cijelokupne javnosti

490
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] i kazneno procesirati ove,

491
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:55,740
[SPEAKER_01] može,

492
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] što govoriš ženo?

493
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

494
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] šta govoriš?

495
00:18:57,619 --> 00:18:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

496
00:18:57,859 --> 00:18:58,200
[SPEAKER_01] samo,

497
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,359
[SPEAKER_01] i pazite šta rade,

498
00:18:59,359 --> 00:19:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] samo u nama revolt izazivaju.

499
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:02,660
[SPEAKER_01] I to je nevjerojatno kako oni,

500
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:03,660
[SPEAKER_01] meni je samo,

501
00:19:03,660 --> 00:19:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] nijem jasno,

502
00:19:04,619 --> 00:19:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] jel toliko ne razumiju narod ulicu

503
00:19:08,019 --> 00:19:09,160
[SPEAKER_01] ili to rade namjerno?

504
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

505
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] to je pitanje.

506
00:19:10,079 --> 00:19:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ova ekipa u Kninu,

507
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,119
[SPEAKER_01] na Uluju,

508
00:19:13,119 --> 00:19:14,500
[SPEAKER_01] sa Hosovom zastavom,

509
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:15,779
[SPEAKER_01] koju je apsolutno podržavam.

510
00:19:15,779 --> 00:19:16,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

511
00:19:16,059 --> 00:19:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] momci navijači,

512
00:19:21,180 --> 00:19:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] funcuta,

513
00:19:21,619 --> 00:19:22,720
[SPEAKER_01] kohorte i tako dalje.

514
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

515
00:19:23,460 --> 00:19:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] to vam je prkos,

516
00:19:24,519 --> 00:19:26,160
[SPEAKER_01] bilo je hrvatskih zastava iz desetke.

517
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,079
[SPEAKER_01] A kome prkose?

518
00:19:27,079 --> 00:19:28,500
[SPEAKER_01] Svima onima,

519
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] koji iz dana u dane

520
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:31,980
[SPEAKER_01] prestaju skakati po glavi,

521
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:32,759
[SPEAKER_01] Hosu,

522
00:19:32,759 --> 00:19:33,799
[SPEAKER_01] braniteljima,

523
00:19:33,799 --> 00:19:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] to se stalno događa.

524
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] Koji problematiziraju taj pozdrav?

525
00:19:37,079 --> 00:19:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

526
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:41,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zar to ne bi trebalo biti normalno i legitimno?

527
00:19:41,059 --> 00:19:42,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da, naravno,

528
00:19:42,019 --> 00:19:43,240
[SPEAKER_01] ali isto legitimno.

529
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ali možda oni doživljaju

530
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] i da oni njima skaču po glavi,

531
00:19:46,059 --> 00:19:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

532
00:19:46,339 --> 00:19:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] ono nezgodno je to.

533
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] Demokracija.

534
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,799
[SPEAKER_01] Demokracija.

535
00:19:51,180 --> 00:19:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] da, da, da.

536
00:19:51,819 --> 00:19:53,660
[SPEAKER_00] Zar vi doista mislite da u ovom trenutku

537
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] u Hrvatskoj

538
00:19:54,839 --> 00:19:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] su katolička crkva,

539
00:19:57,980 --> 00:19:58,839
[SPEAKER_00] vjeronauk,

540
00:19:58,839 --> 00:19:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] branitelji,

541
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:00,740
[SPEAKER_00] mislim i na

542
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:03,240
[SPEAKER_00] realan život,

543
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] na

544
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] mirovine,

545
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] prava,

546
00:20:06,619 --> 00:20:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] vjeronauku školama,

547
00:20:08,079 --> 00:20:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] crkve,

548
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] mislim i sve ugrožena kategorija.

549
00:20:11,619 --> 00:20:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] Imam vam odgovor.

550
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:12,700
[SPEAKER_00] Doista.

551
00:20:12,700 --> 00:20:13,240
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

552
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:15,339
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam potpuno uvjeren

553
00:20:15,339 --> 00:20:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] da mi na desnom spektru

554
00:20:17,759 --> 00:20:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] želimo živjeti u 2025.

555
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,819
[SPEAKER_01] i ako tko govori

556
00:20:20,819 --> 00:20:22,140
[SPEAKER_01] o malim i rovinama,

557
00:20:22,140 --> 00:20:23,299
[SPEAKER_01] ako se ko tukao

558
00:20:23,299 --> 00:20:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] s vladajućima

559
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] oko prava radnika,

560
00:20:25,119 --> 00:20:26,579
[SPEAKER_01] naše grmoje,

561
00:20:26,579 --> 00:20:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] mene tamo,

562
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] spavali smo pet dana

563
00:20:29,059 --> 00:20:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] u prosvjedu sa seljacima

564
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:31,220
[SPEAKER_01] u županji.

565
00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:31,680
